<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{subject}}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #2196F3;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>{{title}}</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        {{{body}}}
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>Trân trọng,<br>Đội ngũ NestJS App</p>
        <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #999;">
            Email này được gửi tự động, vui lòng không trả lời.
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
